# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
@angular/core

### Is this a regression?

Yes, it works before Ivy.

https://stackblitz.com/edit/angular-oqwzqb?file=src%2Fapp%2Fhostbinding-test.directive.ts

### Description

This doesn't work like it used to be. 
```ts
@HostBinding("style")
style: SafeStyle = this.sanitizer.bypassSecurityTrustStyle(
    "background: red; color: white; display: block;"
  );
```

It does work if we do it like this 

```ts
@HostBinding("style.background")
styleBackground: SafeStyle = this.sanitizer.bypassSecurityTrustStyle("red");
```

## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction

https://github.com/maxisam/angular-ivy-style-issue 

if we set "enableIvy: false", it works.

